  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Can You Escape Granny's Sinister House?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dive into a heart-pounding horror experience where every decision could be your last.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏚️ UNCOVER THE MYSTERIES OF A HOUSE TEEMING WITH SECRETS AND PERILS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Environments:</strong> Traverse from shadowy basements to ominous attics, each filled with secrets waiting to be discovered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Visuals:</strong> Stunning graphics and meticulous details draw you deeper into the chilling atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/fe0dbbeab65e1eccfa666f09c301c056.poster.avif?t=1774355255\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/fe0dbbeab65e1eccfa666f09c301c056.webm?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/fe0dbbeab65e1eccfa666f09c301c056.mp4?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 SOLVE DIVERSE PUZZLES AND OVERCOME CHALLENGES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engaging Brain Teasers:</strong> Solve the cuckoo clock puzzle, use the metal detector to find hidden items, and test your aim in the attic shooting gallery. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vital Tools:</strong> Locate essential items like the flare gun and phone to outsmart Granny and secure your escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/d7b1aed2f4b0e5997d8ea0fcf6d49586.poster.avif?t=1774355255\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/d7b1aed2f4b0e5997d8ea0fcf6d49586.webm?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/d7b1aed2f4b0e5997d8ea0fcf6d49586.mp4?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚪 CHOOSE YOUR ROUTE TO FREEDOM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flee by Car:</strong> Assemble the missing parts and speed away from terror. <br><strong>Summon Rescue:</strong> Signal for help using the flare gun and phone to bring authorities to your aid. <br><strong>Break Through the Front Door:</strong> Uncover keys and tools to make your escape through the main entrance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/2cf722b69a802a18891ebfd43754d1cf.poster.avif?t=1774355255\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/2cf722b69a802a18891ebfd43754d1cf.webm?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/2cf722b69a802a18891ebfd43754d1cf.mp4?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 HEART-STOPPING GAMEPLAY AGAINST A RELENTLESS FOE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adaptive AI Enemy:</strong> Granny hears every whisper, senses your presence, and pursues you without mercy.<br><strong>Advanced Stealth Mechanics:</strong> Move silently, peek around corners, and use the environment to stay hidden. <br><strong>Unpredictable Threats:</strong> Stay vigilant—danger can strike unexpectedly from anywhere.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/8df8606710fe2658dc7e2dacbaf563fa.poster.avif?t=1774355255\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/8df8606710fe2658dc7e2dacbaf563fa.webm?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/8df8606710fe2658dc7e2dacbaf563fa.mp4?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔊 IMMERSIVE AUDIO THAT AMPLIFIES THE HORROR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Sounds:</strong> Realistic sound effects amplify the suspense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adaptive Soundtrack:</strong> Dynamic music intensifies during critical moments, pulling you deeper into the experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/6eb5414d07625f0631339cfddd608212.poster.avif?t=1774355255\" width=600 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/6eb5414d07625f0631339cfddd608212.webm?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110820/extras/6eb5414d07625f0631339cfddd608212.mp4?t=1774355255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are You Ready to Face Your Fears?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Buy now and dive into the nightmare. Your escape begins here.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👥 